        <span id="BookReviewTitle" class="BookReviewTitle">Practical Web Traffic Analysis: Standards, Privacy, Techniques, and Results</span>
        <div class="ItemDetail">By
          <span id="Authors">Alex Poon, Ben Pearce, Peter Comber, Peter Fletcher</span></div>
